<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Tara Rose Salon — Khalifa Branch Reviews</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Cormorant+Garamond:ital,wght@0,300;0,400;0,600;1,300;1,400&family=DM+Sans:wght@300;400;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
  :root {
    --rose: #c9856a;
    --rose-light: #f5ebe6;
    --rose-deep: #a0614a;
    --gold: #c4a882;
    --dark: #1a1410;
    --mid: #4a3f38;
    --light: #fdf8f5;
    --cream: #f7efe8;
    --border: #e8d8cc;
  }

  * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }

  body {
    font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;
    background: var(--light);
    color: var(--dark);
    min-height: 100vh;
  }

  /* HEADER */
  header {
    background: var(--dark);
    padding: 60px 40px 50px;
    text-align: center;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  header::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background: radial-gradient(ellipse at 50% 0%, rgba(201,133,106,0.25) 0%, transparent 70%);
  }

  .header-inner { position: relative; z-index: 1; }

  .branch-tag {
    display: inline-block;
    font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 0.3em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--rose);
    border: 1px solid rgba(201,133,106,0.4);
    padding: 6px 18px;
    border-radius: 100px;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }

  header h1 {
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
    font-size: clamp(36px, 6vw, 64px);
    font-weight: 300;
    color: #fff;
    letter-spacing: 0.02em;
    line-height: 1.1;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }

  header h1 em {
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--rose);
  }

  header p {
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.45);
    font-size: 13px;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    margin-top: 16px;
  }

  /* STATS BAR */
  .stats-bar {
    background: var(--cream);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
    padding: 28px 40px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 48px;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .stat {
    text-align: center;
  }

  .stat-value {
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
    font-size: 32px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--rose-deep);
    line-height: 1;
  }

  .stat-label {
    font-size: 11px;
    letter-spacing: 0.15em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--mid);
    margin-top: 4px;
  }

  .stat-divider {
    width: 1px;
    height: 40px;
    background: var(--border);
  }

  .breakdown {
    display: flex;
    gap: 6px;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .breakdown-pill {
    padding: 4px 12px;
    border-radius: 100px;
    font-size: 12px;
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  .pill-green { background: #e8f5e9; color: #2e7d32; }
  .pill-yellow { background: #fff8e1; color: #f57f17; }
  .pill-red { background: #fce4ec; color: #c62828; }

  /* FILTER TABS */
  .filter-bar {
    padding: 24px 40px;
    display: flex;
    gap: 10px;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
    background: #fff;
    position: sticky;
    top: 0;
    z-index: 10;
    box-shadow: 0 2px 12px rgba(0,0,0,0.04);
  }

  .filter-btn {
    padding: 8px 20px;
    border-radius: 100px;
    border: 1.5px solid var(--border);
    background: transparent;
    font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;
    font-size: 13px;
    color: var(--mid);
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: all 0.2s;
    font-weight: 400;
  }

  .filter-btn:hover, .filter-btn.active {
    background: var(--dark);
    border-color: var(--dark);
    color: #fff;
  }

  .filter-btn.active-pos { background: #2e7d32; border-color: #2e7d32; color: #fff; }
  .filter-btn.active-neg { background: #c62828; border-color: #c62828; color: #fff; }

  /* MAIN CONTENT */
  .main {
    max-width: 960px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 48px 24px;
  }

  /* SECTION HEADERS */
  .section-header {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 16px;
    margin-bottom: 28px;
    margin-top: 48px;
  }

  .section-header:first-child { margin-top: 0; }

  .section-icon {
    width: 40px;
    height: 40px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    font-size: 18px;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .icon-pos { background: #e8f5e9; }
  .icon-neg { background: #fce4ec; }
  .icon-neu { background: #fff8e1; }

  .section-title {
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
    font-size: 26px;
    font-weight: 400;
    color: var(--dark);
  }

  .section-count {
    margin-left: auto;
    font-size: 12px;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--mid);
    background: var(--cream);
    padding: 4px 14px;
    border-radius: 100px;
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
  }

  /* REVIEW CARDS */
  .reviews-grid {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 16px;
  }

  .review-card {
    background: #fff;
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 16px;
    padding: 24px 28px;
    transition: box-shadow 0.2s, transform 0.2s;
    position: relative;
  }

  .review-card:hover {
    box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
    transform: translateY(-2px);
  }

  .review-card.negative {
    border-left: 3px solid #e57373;
  }

  .review-card.positive {
    border-left: 3px solid #81c784;
  }

  .review-top {
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 14px;
    margin-bottom: 14px;
  }

  .reviewer-avatar {
    width: 42px;
    height: 42px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--rose), var(--gold));
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    color: #fff;
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
    font-size: 18px;
    font-weight: 600;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .reviewer-info { flex: 1; }

  .reviewer-name {
    font-weight: 500;
    font-size: 15px;
    color: var(--dark);
    margin-bottom: 2px;
  }

  .review-meta {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 10px;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .review-date {
    font-size: 12px;
    color: #999;
  }

  .stars {
    display: flex;
    gap: 2px;
  }

  .star {
    font-size: 13px;
  }

  .star.filled { color: #f4b942; }
  .star.empty { color: #ddd; }

  .source-badge {
    width: 20px;
    height: 20px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: #4285f4;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #fff;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .review-text {
    font-size: 14px;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: #555;
  }

  /* STYLIST TAGS */
  .stylist-tags {
    margin-top: 12px;
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 6px;
  }

  .stylist-tag {
    font-size: 11px;
    padding: 3px 10px;
    background: var(--rose-light);
    color: var(--rose-deep);
    border-radius: 100px;
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 0.03em;
  }

  /* FOOTER */
  footer {
    background: var(--dark);
    text-align: center;
    padding: 32px;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.3);
    font-size: 12px;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
  }

  footer span { color: var(--rose); }

  /* Separator */
  .section-sep {
    height: 1px;
    background: linear-gradient(to right, transparent, var(--border), transparent);
    margin: 8px 0 32px;
  }

  @media (max-width: 600px) {
    .stats-bar { gap: 24px; padding: 20px; }
    .stat-divider { display: none; }
    header { padding: 40px 20px 36px; }
    .filter-bar { padding: 16px 20px; }
    .main { padding: 32px 16px; }
    .review-card { padding: 18px 16px; }
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<header>
  <div class="header-inner">
    <div class="branch-tag">Khalifa City Branch</div>
    <h1>Tara Rose <em>Salon</em></h1>
    <p>Client Reviews &amp; Testimonials — Google</p>
  </div>
</header>

<div class="stats-bar">
  <div class="stat">
    <div class="stat-value">4.8 / 5</div>
    <div class="stat-label">Google Rating</div>
  </div>
  <div class="stat-divider"></div>
  <div class="stat">
    <div class="stat-value">874</div>
    <div class="stat-label">Total Reviews</div>
  </div>
  <div class="stat-divider"></div>
  <div class="stat">
    <div class="stat-label" style="margin-bottom:8px;">Reputation Breakdown</div>
    <div class="breakdown">
      <span class="breakdown-pill pill-green">95% Positive</span>
      <span class="breakdown-pill pill-yellow">1% Neutral</span>
      <span class="breakdown-pill pill-red">4% Negative</span>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="filter-bar">
  <button class="filter-btn active" onclick="filterReviews('all', this)">All Reviews</button>
  <button class="filter-btn" onclick="filterReviews('positive', this)">⭐ 5-Star</button>
  <button class="filter-btn" onclick="filterReviews('negative', this)">👎 Low Ratings</button>
</div>

<div class="main">

  <!-- 5 STAR SECTION -->
  <div class="section-header" data-section="positive">
    <div class="section-icon icon-pos">⭐</div>
    <div class="section-title">5-Star Reviews</div>
    <div class="section-count">42 reviews</div>
  </div>
  <div class="section-sep"></div>
  <div class="reviews-grid" id="positive-reviews">

    <div class="review-card positive" data-rating="5">
      <div class="review-top">
        <div class="reviewer-avatar">R</div>
        <div class="reviewer-info">
          <div class="reviewer-name">Richa Unkule</div>
          <div class="review-meta">
            <div class="stars"><span class="star filled">★</span><span class="star filled">★</span><span class="star filled">★</span><span class="star filled">★</span><span class="star filled">★</span></div>
            <span class="review-date">3 days ago</span>
            <div class="source-badge">G</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="review-text">I always get my haircut from Kate! She is such wizard with hair!! My bob always looks gorgeous after she's cut my hair ❤️</div>
      <div class="stylist-tags"><span class="stylist-tag">Kate</span></div>
    </div>

    <div class="review-card positive" data-rating="5">
      <div class="review-top">
        <div class="reviewer-avatar">M</div>
        <div class="reviewer-info">
          <div class="reviewer-name">mytha h</div>
          <div class="review-meta">
            <div class="stars"><span class="star filled">★</span><span class="star filled">★</span><span class="star filled">★</span><span class="star filled">★</span><span class="star filled">★</span></div>
            <span class="review-date">5 days ago</span>
            <div class="source-badge">G</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="review-text">Ms. Lyn (junior stylist) did my hairstyle its perfeccttt. She is very precise and she knows what shes doing. They listen to you 100%. I tried with Ms. May (junior hair stylist too) she once did my highlights and also hairstyle. She is also very nice precise and know her job very well. Service 100/100 - very clean. Good music</div>
      <div class="stylist-tags"><span class="stylist-tag">Lyn</span><span class="stylist-tag">May</span></div>
    </div>

    <div class="review-card positive" data-rating="5">
      <div class="review-top">
        <div class="reviewer-avatar">M</div>
        <div class="reviewer-info">
          <div class="reviewer-name">mathi nilla</div>
          <div class="review-meta">
            <div class="stars"><span class="star filled">★</span><span class="star filled">★</span><span class="star filled">★</span><span class="star filled">★</span><span class="star filled">★</span></div>
            <span class="review-date">6 days ago</span>
            <div class="source-badge">G</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="review-text">May did my protein hair treatment, and it doesn't have a strong chemical smell. It's lightweight on my hair, and my hair feels more manageable and frizz-free and she's so sweet 😊</div>
      <div class="stylist-tags"><span class="stylist-tag">May</span></div>
    </div>

    <div class="review-card positive" data-rating="5">
      <div class="review-top">
        <div class="reviewer-avatar">S</div>
        <div class="reviewer-info">
          <div class="reviewer-name">Sandy Savo</div>
          <div class="review-meta">
            <div class="stars"><span class="star filled">★</span><span class="star filled">★</span><span class="star filled">★</span><span class="star filled">★</span><span class="star filled">★</span></div>
            <span class="review-date">8 days ago</span>
            <div class="source-badge">G</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="review-text">A consistently exceptional experience. This salon is the definition of professionalism, with a genuine focus on customer experience in every detail. I've been using their services for the past two years, and they have never once fallen short. What truly sets them apart is their people. When a business recruits talented staff and takes real care of them, the result is felt instantly by clients. The positive attitude, the warmth, the pride in their work, it all comes through naturally. A place that gets it right, every time. Every visit is a reminder of how thoughtful service and a happy team create an atmosphere you actually look forward to returning to.</div>
    </div>

    <div class="review-card positive" data-rating="5">
      <div class="review-top">
        <div class="reviewer-avatar">F</div>
        <div class="reviewer-info">
          <div class="reviewer-name">Fathima. A</div>
          <div class="review-meta">
            <div class="stars"><span class="star filled">★</span><span class="star filled">★</span><span class="star filled">★</span><span class="star filled">★</span><span class="star filled">★</span></div>
            <span class="review-date">8 days ago</span>
            <div class="source-badge">G</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="review-text">Excellent service. Highly recommended</div>
    </div>

    <div class="review-card positive" data-rating="5">
      <div class="review-top">
        <div class="reviewer-avatar">I</div>
        <div class="reviewer-info">
          <div class="reviewer-name">I "leu"</div>
          <div class="review-meta">
            <div class="stars"><span class="star filled">★</span><span class="star filled">★</span><span class="star filled">★</span><span class="star filled">★</span><span class="star filled">★</span></div>
            <span class="review-date">13 days ago</span>
            <div class="source-badge">G</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="review-text">Lynn is absolutely amazing at styling my hair! I try to request her as much as possible as she is the only stylist I've ever went to who does my hair exactly like I imagine it to be. Keep in mind, I have very long and VERY layered hair, not only does her styling stick, but she also nails it every time without me showing her a photo! I've been a reliable customer here for years and plan on it staying that way 🥰🥰🥰</div>
      <div class="stylist-tags"><span class="stylist-tag">Lynn</span></div>
    </div>

    <div class="review-card positive" data-rating="5">
      <div class="review-top">
        <div class="reviewer-avatar">F</div>
        <div class="reviewer-info">
          <div class="reviewer-name">Futtaim AlT.</div>
          <div class="review-meta">
            <div class="stars"><span class="star filled">★</span><span class="star filled">★</span><span class="star filled">★</span><span class="star filled">★</span><span class="star filled">★</span></div>
            <span class="review-date">14 days ago</span>
            <div class="source-badge">G</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="review-text">Amazing hair services 😍🔥 a very friendly staff. I did my hair with Lynn ❤️ she was amazing and i really loved the final look 😍🔥 Highly recommended 😎</div>
      <div class="stylist-tags"><span class="stylist-tag">Lynn</span></div>
    </div>

    <div class="review-card positive" data-rating="5">
      <div class="review-top">
        <div class="reviewer-avatar">M</div>
        <div class="reviewer-info">
          <div class="reviewer-name">Mira</div>
          <div class="review-meta">
            <div class="stars"><span class="star filled">★</span><span class="star filled">★</span><span class="star filled">★</span><span class="star filled">★</span><span class="star filled">★</span></div>
            <span class="review-date">16 days ago</span>
            <div class="source-badge">G</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="review-text">I had a great experience at Tara Rose Salon! The staff were all very friendly and welcoming. Lynn did my hair and she was so kind and professional. I did the ABC treatment and I'm really happy with the results—my hair feels so much healthier and looks amazing. I'll definitely be coming back!</div>
      <div class="stylist-tags"><span class="stylist-tag">Lynn</span></div>
    </div>

    <div class="review-card positive" data-rating="5">
      <div class="review-top">
        <div class="reviewer-avatar">M</div>
        <div class="reviewer-info">
          <div class="reviewer-name">mouza almansoori</div>
          <div class="review-meta">
            <div class="stars"><span class="star filled">★</span><span class="star filled">★</span><span class="star filled">★</span><span class="star filled">★</span><span class="star filled">★</span></div>
            <span class="review-date">19 days ago</span>
            <div class="source-badge">G</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="review-text"><em style="color:#aaa;">(No written review)</em></div>
    </div>

    <div class="review-card positive" data-rating="5">
      <div class="review-top">
        <div class="reviewer-avatar">M</div>
        <div class="reviewer-info">
          <div class="reviewer-name">Mary Joy David Reyes</div>
          <div class="review-meta">
            <div class="stars"><span class="star filled">★</span><span class="star filled">★</span><span class="star filled">★</span><span class="star filled">★</span><span class="star filled">★</span></div>
            <span class="review-date">19 days ago</span>
            <div class="source-badge">G</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="review-text">I recently had my hair colored by Ms. Lyn Padilla in Tara Rose Salon Khalifa branch, and the results were absolutely fantastic. She did an incredible job with the color, achieving the exact look I was hoping for with precision and skill. What truly set the experience apart, however, was her attentiveness and care. From the moment the service began until the very end, she was consistently making sure I was comfortable and well-taken care of. It is rare to find a stylist who combines such high-level technical talent with such a genuine, caring approach. I highly recommend Ms. Lyn for anyone looking for professional hair coloring and a truly pleasant salon experience.</div>
      <div class="stylist-tags"><span class="stylist-tag">Lyn Padilla</span></div>
    </div>

    <div class="review-card positive" data-rating="5">
      <div class="review-top">
        <div class="reviewer-avatar">R</div>
        <div class="reviewer-info">
          <div class="reviewer-name">Raya Almansoori</div>
          <div class="review-meta">
            <div class="stars"><span class="star filled">★</span><span class="star filled">★</span><span class="star filled">★</span><span class="star filled">★</span><span class="star filled">★</span></div>
            <span class="review-date">23 days ago</span>
            <div class="source-badge">G</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="review-text">I had such a lovely experience at Tara Rose Salon & Fratelli Barbershop 🩶 The service was amazing and the staff were very friendly and professional. A special thank you to Kylie for her great work — I really loved the result! ✨ Highly recommend and will definitely come back again 🥰</div>
      <div class="stylist-tags"><span class="stylist-tag">Kylie</span></div>
    </div>

    <div class="review-card positive" data-rating="5">
      <div class="review-top">
        <div class="reviewer-avatar">A</div>
        <div class="reviewer-info">
          <div class="reviewer-name">an</div>
          <div class="review-meta">
            <div class="stars"><span class="star filled">★</span><span class="star filled">★</span><span class="star filled">★</span><span class="star filled">★</span><span class="star filled">★</span></div>
            <span class="review-date">25 days ago</span>
            <div class="source-badge">G</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="review-text">I had an amazing experience with May! I went in for a full balayage and the results are absolutely perfect exactly what I was looking for. Not only is she incredibly talented, but she is also so kind and made the whole appointment such a pleasure. I highly recommend her if you're looking for a flawless color and a great experience!</div>
      <div class="stylist-tags"><span class="stylist-tag">May</span></div>
    </div>

    <div class="review-card positive" data-rating="5">
      <div class="review-top">
        <div class="reviewer-avatar">A</div>
        <div class="reviewer-info">
          <div class="reviewer-name">Areej A</div>
          <div class="review-meta">
            <div class="stars"><span class="star filled">★</span><span class="star filled">★</span><span class="star filled">★</span><span class="star filled">★</span><span class="star filled">★</span></div>
            <span class="review-date">a month ago</span>
            <div class="source-badge">G</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="review-text"><em style="color:#aaa;">(No written review)</em></div>
    </div>

    <div class="review-card positive" data-rating="5">
      <div class="review-top">
        <div class="reviewer-avatar">S</div>
        <div class="reviewer-info">
          <div class="reviewer-name">Sara A</div>
          <div class="review-meta">
            <div class="stars"><span class="star filled">★</span><span class="star filled">★</span><span class="star filled">★</span><span class="star filled">★</span><span class="star filled">★</span></div>
            <span class="review-date">a month ago</span>
            <div class="source-badge">G</div>
          </div>
        </div>
